itunes:title: Winning with the Hand You’re Dealt - Part 4
title: Winning with the Hand You’re Dealt - Part 4
description: The freedom to choose is our greatest blessing from God, but that also means we may make foolish choices that harm us and harm the people around us. In this broadcast, Pastor Rick helps you understand that your identity is shaped by your choices. He shows you how to make choices that will positively affect the rest of your life.
